WEBVTT

00:01.434 --> 00:03.607
APRIL: Andy and Leslie
sent us care packages.

00:03.937 --> 00:06.508
"Hey,Ben, just a few things
to remind you of home.

00:06.573 --> 00:07.608
"Love, Leslie."

00:08.173 --> 00:13.021
Ah. Waffle Mix. J.J.'s Diner mug.
New pajamas.

00:13.079 --> 00:15.218
Wow, there's a lot
of stuff in here.

00:15.448 --> 00:17.291
"Box one of twelve"?

00:18.818 --> 00:20.627
"April, here's something
to help you remember

00:20.687 --> 00:22.428
"our three-legged dog,
Champion."

00:22.489 --> 00:23.593
Oh, that's cute.

00:23.656 --> 00:25.567
"Also, you are way
better at laundry.

00:25.625 --> 00:28.128
"Can you please do mine
and send it back to me?

00:28.194 --> 00:30.606
"Thanks. Love you. Mouse Rat rules.
Love, Andy."

00:30.663 --> 00:31.664
Less cute.

00:31.731 --> 00:32.903
"P.S. Please hurry.

00:32.966 --> 00:35.572
"I've been wearing a bandana as
underwear for three days now."

00:35.668 --> 00:37.545
Look,
there's a picture.

00:37.737 --> 00:38.738
BEN: Ah.

00:38.905 --> 00:40.111
That's horrifying.

00:40.273 --> 00:41.377
(sums)

00:43.009 --> 00:44.750
(VOICE BREAKING)
I love him so much.

